title: [The early abdominal pregnancy--case report].
abstract: The abdominal ectopic pregnancies are 1-1.4% of all ectopic pregnancies. In this article we presents the case of 27-year-old patient in early abdominal pregnancy, situated in parietal peritoneum. This case justifies the need to take into account possibility of abdominal pregnancy in case of suspicion of ectopic pregnancy.
categories: Female Urogenital Diseases and Pregnancy Complications
